==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unseconded
<hw>Un*sec"ond*ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
seconded; not supported, aided, or assisted; <as>as, the motion was
<ex>unseconded</ex>; the attempt was <ex>unseconded</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not exemplified a second time.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Strange and <xex>unseconded</xex> shapes of
worms.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Sir T. Browne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unsecret</ent>⟦br⟧
